    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust to be found. It drives like a dream and still has that wonderful new-car feel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out, I'd love to chat more about it!",
